This is a python package that generates apache airflow configuration code for supporting azure active directory sso tokens.

## Installation

```
pip install airflow-azure-sso
```

## Usage

```
from airflow_azure_sso import generate_airflow_config

generate_airflow_config(
    client_id="<client_id>",
    tenant_id="<tenant_id>",
    client_secret="<client_secret>",
    airflow_config_path="<airflow_config_path>",
    airflow_config_file="<airflow_config_file>",
    airflow_config_section="<airflow_config_section>",
    airflow_config_key="<airflow_config_key>",
    airflow_config_value="<airflow_config_value>",
    airflow_config_comment="<airflow_config_comment>",
)
```
